Settlements of Kenya

settlements

Format

A SpatialPointsDataFrame with 2675 features:

Z__

Z__

UFI

Unique feature identifier (UTM)

UNI

Unique name identifier (UTM)

DLAT

Latitude coordinates (degrees)

DLONG

Longitude coordinates (degrees)

LAT

Latitude coordinate (UTM)

LONG

Longitude coordinate (UTM)

MGRS

Military Grid Reference System code

FC

Feature code

DSG

Description code

PC

Place code

CC1

Country code 1

ADM1

Administrative level 1 code

ADM2

Administrative level 2 code

DIM

DIM

CC2

Country code 2

NT

NT

LC

LC

SHORT_FORM

Short form

GENERIC

Generic

SORT_NAME

Sort name

FULL_NAME

Full name

FULL_NAME_

Full name

NEWDLAT

New latitude (degrees)

NEWDLONG

New longitude (degrees)

CODE

Code

DISTRICT

District name

REGION

Region name

LOCATION

Location name

SUB_LOCATI

Sub-location name

Source

https://data.humdata.org/dataset/kenya-settlements-0
